h1 Recent Questions

- if user_signed_in?
  = form_for Question.new do |f|
    = render partial: 'form', locals: { f: f }

- @questions.each do |question|
  p = link_to question.title, question
  p = question.category.name
  p = pluralize question.answers.size, 'answer'

  p
    =' question.user.username
    ' asked
    =' distance_of_time_in_words_to_now question.created_at
    | ago
